Description:
Dell OptiPlex 3000 3080 Desktop Computer - Intel Core i5 10th Gen i5-10505 Hexa-core (6 Core) 3.20 GHz - 8 GB RAM DDR4 SDRAM - 256 GB NVMe M.2 PCI Express M.2 SSD - Small Form Factor - Black - Windows 10 Pro - Intel DDR4 SDRAM - DVD-Writer - English Keyboard - 200 W 8GB 256GB SSD W10 VGA
Essential business desktops.
Essential business tower and small form factor desktops that deliver best-in-class security and manageability. With 10th Gen Intel® processors.
Operating System l Available with Windows 10 Pro - for a smooth, versatile PC experience.
Work smart l Flexible configurations: Embrace new productivity features at the same affordable price you've come to expect. With multiple form factors, you'll find a desktop that works perfectly within your workspace.
Stay Cool: Utilizing the new cooling design of the front bezel, the 3080 maximizes air intake to keep your system temperature down.
Small size, small upkeep: Easier access to parts without removing front bezel delivers simplified maintenance with its toolless features.
Uncompromising productivity l Power through your work: Built with 10th Generation Intel® architecture, and supports Celeron®, Pentium®, Core i3 and i5 processors for uncompromising performance and up to 64GB 2666 MHz DDR4 RAM.
Next-Gen graphics: Tackle the most graphically demanding workloads with the latest NVIDIA® and AMD discrete graphics.

High Connectivity: Connect with ease with native DisplayPort and HDMI, and optional VGA, HDMI 2.0b, or 2nd DisplayPort.
Intelligence built in. Modernization built on.
We know that having the right device is just the start to a great workday. Employees need intelligent, intuitive and responsive experiences that allow them to work productively and without interruption. According to research, 1 out of every 4 users would question their job and the company they work for if they had a negative experience with their technology.
Dell Technologies Unified Workspace is transforming the employee experience and ensuring IT has proactive, predictive and automated solutions to deliver on the promise of a modern workday, while simplifying their ability to deploy, secure, manage and support their environment.

Deploy: ProDeploy in the Unified Workspace allows IT to move away from traditional, high-touch, manual deployment, and instead, ship devices preconfigured with company apps and settings from the Dell factory directly to their end users-having end users up and working on day one.

Secure: Dell Trusted Devices provide a foundation to a modern workforce environment with invisible and seamless protection to ensure smarter, faster experiences. End users stay productive and IT stays confident with modern security solutions for the Dell Trusted Device.

Manage: Dell Client Command Suite + VMware Workspace ONE offers integrated capabilities that deliver a unified endpoint management experience for IT, enabling them to manage firmware, OS, and apps from one console, while also creating seamless experiences for end users.

Support: ProSupport resolves hardware issues up to 11x faster than the competition. ProSupport for PCs offers 24x7 access to in-region ProSupport engineers who contact IT when critical issues arise, so you can focus on what's next, not what just happened.

ProSupport Plus helps IT stay a step ahead and virtually eliminate unplanned downtime due to hardware issues. You get all the capabilities of ProSupport, as well as AI-driven alerts to prevent failures and repairs for accidents.

Dell Chromebook 11 3000 3100 11.6" Touchscreen 2 in 1 Chromebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - Intel Celeron N4020 Dual-core (2 Core) - 4 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Black - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics - English Keyboard - 13 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1DIMMS 32GB EMMC TOUCH 3C DC WFC
Learning without boundaries
An 11-inch 2-in-1 with best-in-class durability and up to 13 hours of battery life empowers students to learn and collaborate.
Operating System
Operating system - Google Chrome OS
Designed to last beyond the bell
The Chromebook 3000 Series is rigorously tested to endure the school day and beyond. Students can learn uninterrupted with tamper- and spill-resistant keyboards and a long battery life.
Tested to endure the school day
Uncompromised durability: Rigorously tested beyond MIL-STD standards, the Chromebook 3100 2-in-1 keeps up with the entire school day and then some. It's tested to survive 5,000 free fall micro-drops and 30-inch drops onto steel, while rubberized edges minimize impacts from drops and bumps.

Survives spills: Students can learn, discover and share without worry thanks to the spill- and tamper-resistant keyboard that withstands up to 12 ounces of liquid. Plus, its top mounted design ensures the entire palm rest doesn't need to be replaced in case of damage to the keyboard.

Protected ports: Ports are covered and secured with reinforced brackets, and they're tested to ensure students can connect and disconnect as many times as they need.
Enabling learning anytime, anywhere
Group learning made easy: The Chromebook 3100 2-in-1 is designed for interactive learning. It supports up to four modes (flat, tent, tablet or laptop) for viewing and collaborating, while the available world facing camera allows students to take advantage of flipped viewing and recording angles.

Good past the last bell: With up to 13 hours of battery life, this trusty 2-in-1 gets kids through even the longest school days. The USB Type-C™ port supports power and data transfers to keep students connected.

Description:
Samsung Galaxy Tab Active3 Rugged Tablet - 8" WUXGA Octa-core (8 Core) 2.70 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Storage - Android 10 - Black - Samsung Exynos 9810 SoC - Upto 1 TB microSD, microSDXC, microSDHC Supported - 1920 x 1200 - 5 Megapixel Front Camera WI-FI
At a glance
The rugged military-grade design of the Galaxy Tab Active3 gives you the confidence you need to take on any job no matter the conditions. Lighten the load and do it all for the whole workday. It delivers the performance you need to achieve the productivity you want.
Rugged and Ready for Work
Conquer the elements and don't sweat the accidents. Dust, dirt, sand and water won't get in your way with the IP68 rated Galaxy Tab Active3 and its S Pen. It's even MIL-STD-810H compliant, so you can drop it from a height of 1.5M and it'll absorb the shock.

Power for Hours
Power through any project thanks to a long-lasting battery that won't stop until your day does. Need to work even longer? The battery is also fast charging and replaceable, so you won't lose a second in the field. The Galaxy Tab Active3 works in No Battery Mode when it's connected to a dedicated power source making it a great in vehicle or fixed kiosk solution.

Tackle Any Job, In Any Place
The gloves don't have to come off, so your team stays safe and dry while they get more done. With enhanced touch capability settings, they can take advantage of an intuitive touchscreen, even while wearing gloves at work.
Designed to Be Compatible with Your Old Accessories
Reap the benefits of a new tablet without reinvesting in new accessories. The Galaxy Tab Active3 is designed with backwards compatibility in mind by keeping a consistent design and form factor.
Wireless DeX
Do more with a single device. With Samsung Wireless DeX, you can boost productivity and use your Galaxy Tab Active3 like a PC - that way you save money and your team can bring important tools into tough environments without having to haul around multiple devices or even a cable.
Always Connected
Wi-Fi 6 and Dual Antenna MIMO support keep your team connected no matter where they work, even in low coverage areas. Enjoy continuous coverage even in the field with optional LTE connectivity. LTE connectivity plans available from AT&T, Verizon, and T-Mobile.

Customize Your Quick Access
Simplify tasks for your entire team. Whether its launching a critical business application, scanning, or using push to talk. The programmable key of Galaxy Tab Active3 can customize and streamline tasks to a single click.

Mobile Point of Sale
Accept payments on one device without any additional hardware. With Galaxy Tab Active3, you won't need additional card readers to process payments.
Reduce the Learning Curve
Spend less time training and more time doing. Galaxy Tab Active3 features Android 10, a familiar UI, so there's a reduced learning curve, even though it's a new device.

Enterprise Edition, Now for Rugged Tablets
Easily enroll, configure and manage hundreds of devices as if they were one with Tab Enterprise Edition on the Tab Active3. Enterprise Edition includes Knox Suite, complete with three-years of product life cycle support, five years of security maintenance and updates, and three OS updates.

Immersive entertainment you can take anywhere.

Galaxy Tab A7 combines the slim, lightweight design you need, with the immersive entertainment experience you crave. The ultra-widescreen display draws you in to movies and shows while Dolby Atmos surround sound speakers place you in the center of the action. Video calls via the landscape-oriented, front-facing camera help you feel as if you're in the same room with family and friends. And the fast processor, long-lasting battery and robust built-in storage let you enjoy more of the streaming, browsing, music and photos you love.

Made to entertain.
Stream and browse on a 10.4-inch1 ultra-widescreen display designed to bring your content to life without weighing you down. The front-facing, landscape-oriented camera allows you to transition between entertainment and video calls seamlessly.

Big sound for big entertainment
With an enhanced quad speaker system that plays everything in Dolby Atmos surround sound, you'll always feel like you're listening from the front row.

Premium entertainment, on us
With purchase of Galaxy Tab A7, get two months of free YouTube Premium2 and six months of free Spotify Premium.

Do more of what you love.
Powerful processing speeds and upgraded4 memory means you can do more, and keep more, of the things you love: apps, videos, playlists and beyond.

Description:
Asus Chromebook C204 C204MA-YB02-GR 11.6" Rugged Chromebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - Intel Celeron N4020 Dual-core (2 Core) 1.10 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Dark Gray - Intel Chip - Chrome OS - Intel UHD Graphics 600 - 12 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1.1 GHZ 4GB 32G NO TOUCH SCREEN
ASUS Chromebook C204

Tough, compact, school-ready
ASUS Chromebook C204 is designed with one thing in mind: to keep on going however tough the environment gets. Built to meet demanding military-grade standards, the classroom-ready durability reassures teachers and students alike. It's packed with clever features to protect it in the real world, such as the all-round rubber bumper, spill-resistant keyboard and ultratough I/O ports. And with its school day-long battery life and time-saving, easy-to-service modular construction, ASUS Chromebook C204 is ready for anything!
Ultimate rugged design
ASUS Chromebook C204 is built to withstand everyday classroom knocks, bumps, drops and spills without damage. Whether it is dropped from a desk or the dinner table the C204 is built like a tank and will keep on going.
Ready for action
Classrooms can be tough, but ASUS Chromebook C204 is tougher! Built to surpass demanding military-grade MIL-STD-810G durability standards, it's also torture-tested to pass stringent ASUS quality tests. It can withstand occasional drops of up to 120cm -more than standard desk height - and the hinge and I/O ports are fully tested to endure the stresses and strains of everyday use.
Ready, right out of the box
With your Chromebook's operation system - the Chrome OS, you can work smarter and more productively, with robust built-in security and automatic updates.
A little help on your Chromebook with the Google Assistant
Get more done fast with the Google Assistant on your ASUS Chromebook C204. Send an email, find documents, listen to music, access your calendar, or control smart home devices, all without switching screens. Just say "Hey Google" to get started.
All-day learning
With up to 12 hours battery life on a single charge, ASUS Chromebook C204 will last for a full day of classes and more. Students could enjoy continuous and uninterrupted learning without worry of battery life.
Thoughtful design for all ages
ASUS Chromebook C204 is not only rugged, but it's designed to be comfortable for everyone. The long key travel on the keyboard 1.5mm gives much better tactile feedback, for a more responsive and comfortable desktop-like typing experience. Working on the ASUS Chromebook C204 is a pleasure, not a chore.
Stress-free sharing
The 180° lay-flat hinge not only enables easier collaboration when you're in a group, but it also reduces stress on the mechanism too.
Good news for IT staff!
For easy on-site servicing and reduced downtime, ASUS Chromebook C204 has a modular construction that allows key components - such as the keyboard, battery, thermal module and motherboard - to be replaced in minutes using simple tools so that IT administrator could focus on the exact issues and send the device to the students in a short time.

Description:
Dell Chromebook 11 3000 3100 11.6" Touchscreen 2 in 1 Chromebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - Intel Celeron N4020 Dual-core (2 Core) - 4 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Black - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics - English Keyboard - 13 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1DIMMS 32GB EMMC TOUCH 3C DC WFC
Learning without boundaries
An 11-inch 2-in-1 with best-in-class durability and up to 13 hours of battery life empowers students to learn and collaborate.
Operating System
Operating system - Google Chrome OS
Designed to last beyond the bell
The Chromebook 3000 Series is rigorously tested to endure the school day and beyond. Students can learn uninterrupted with tamper- and spill-resistant keyboards and a long battery life.
Tested to endure the school day
Uncompromised durability: Rigorously tested beyond MIL-STD standards, the Chromebook 3100 2-in-1 keeps up with the entire school day and then some. It's tested to survive 5,000 free fall micro-drops and 30-inch drops onto steel, while rubberized edges minimize impacts from drops and bumps.

Survives spills: Students can learn, discover and share without worry thanks to the spill- and tamper-resistant keyboard that withstands up to 12 ounces of liquid. Plus, its top mounted design ensures the entire palm rest doesn't need to be replaced in case of damage to the keyboard.

Protected ports: Ports are covered and secured with reinforced brackets, and they're tested to ensure students can connect and disconnect as many times as they need.
Enabling learning anytime, anywhere
Group learning made easy: The Chromebook 3100 2-in-1 is designed for interactive learning. It supports up to four modes (flat, tent, tablet or laptop) for viewing and collaborating, while the available world facing camera allows students to take advantage of flipped viewing and recording angles.

Good past the last bell: With up to 13 hours of battery life, this trusty 2-in-1 gets kids through even the longest school days. The USB Type-C™ port supports power and data transfers to keep students connected.

Description:
Samsung Galaxy Tab Active3 Rugged Tablet - 8" WUXGA Octa-core (8 Core) 2.70 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Storage - Android 10 - Black - Samsung Exynos 9810 SoC - Upto 1 TB microSD, microSDXC, microSDHC Supported - 1920 x 1200 - 5 Megapixel Front Camera WI-FI
At a glance
The rugged military-grade design of the Galaxy Tab Active3 gives you the confidence you need to take on any job no matter the conditions. Lighten the load and do it all for the whole workday. It delivers the performance you need to achieve the productivity you want.
Rugged and Ready for Work
Conquer the elements and don't sweat the accidents. Dust, dirt, sand and water won't get in your way with the IP68 rated Galaxy Tab Active3 and its S Pen. It's even MIL-STD-810H compliant, so you can drop it from a height of 1.5M and it'll absorb the shock.

Power for Hours
Power through any project thanks to a long-lasting battery that won't stop until your day does. Need to work even longer? The battery is also fast charging and replaceable, so you won't lose a second in the field. The Galaxy Tab Active3 works in No Battery Mode when it's connected to a dedicated power source making it a great in vehicle or fixed kiosk solution.

Tackle Any Job, In Any Place
The gloves don't have to come off, so your team stays safe and dry while they get more done. With enhanced touch capability settings, they can take advantage of an intuitive touchscreen, even while wearing gloves at work.
Designed to Be Compatible with Your Old Accessories
Reap the benefits of a new tablet without reinvesting in new accessories. The Galaxy Tab Active3 is designed with backwards compatibility in mind by keeping a consistent design and form factor.
Wireless DeX
Do more with a single device. With Samsung Wireless DeX, you can boost productivity and use your Galaxy Tab Active3 like a PC - that way you save money and your team can bring important tools into tough environments without having to haul around multiple devices or even a cable.
Always Connected
Wi-Fi 6 and Dual Antenna MIMO support keep your team connected no matter where they work, even in low coverage areas. Enjoy continuous coverage even in the field with optional LTE connectivity. LTE connectivity plans available from AT&T, Verizon, and T-Mobile.

Customize Your Quick Access
Simplify tasks for your entire team. Whether its launching a critical business application, scanning, or using push to talk. The programmable key of Galaxy Tab Active3 can customize and streamline tasks to a single click.

Mobile Point of Sale
Accept payments on one device without any additional hardware. With Galaxy Tab Active3, you won't need additional card readers to process payments.
Reduce the Learning Curve
Spend less time training and more time doing. Galaxy Tab Active3 features Android 10, a familiar UI, so there's a reduced learning curve, even though it's a new device.

Enterprise Edition, Now for Rugged Tablets
Easily enroll, configure and manage hundreds of devices as if they were one with Tab Enterprise Edition on the Tab Active3. Enterprise Edition includes Knox Suite, complete with three-years of product life cycle support, five years of security maintenance and updates, and three OS updates.

Immersive entertainment you can take anywhere.

Galaxy Tab A7 combines the slim, lightweight design you need, with the immersive entertainment experience you crave. The ultra-widescreen display draws you in to movies and shows while Dolby Atmos surround sound speakers place you in the center of the action. Video calls via the landscape-oriented, front-facing camera help you feel as if you're in the same room with family and friends. And the fast processor, long-lasting battery and robust built-in storage let you enjoy more of the streaming, browsing, music and photos you love.

Made to entertain.
Stream and browse on a 10.4-inch1 ultra-widescreen display designed to bring your content to life without weighing you down. The front-facing, landscape-oriented camera allows you to transition between entertainment and video calls seamlessly.

Big sound for big entertainment
With an enhanced quad speaker system that plays everything in Dolby Atmos surround sound, you'll always feel like you're listening from the front row.

Premium entertainment, on us
With purchase of Galaxy Tab A7, get two months of free YouTube Premium2 and six months of free Spotify Premium.

Do more of what you love.
Powerful processing speeds and upgraded4 memory means you can do more, and keep more, of the things you love: apps, videos, playlists and beyond.

Description:
Asus Chromebook C204 C204MA-YB02-GR 11.6" Rugged Chromebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - Intel Celeron N4020 Dual-core (2 Core) 1.10 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Dark Gray - Intel Chip - Chrome OS - Intel UHD Graphics 600 - 12 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1.1 GHZ 4GB 32G NO TOUCH SCREEN
ASUS Chromebook C204

Tough, compact, school-ready
ASUS Chromebook C204 is designed with one thing in mind: to keep on going however tough the environment gets. Built to meet demanding military-grade standards, the classroom-ready durability reassures teachers and students alike. It's packed with clever features to protect it in the real world, such as the all-round rubber bumper, spill-resistant keyboard and ultratough I/O ports. And with its school day-long battery life and time-saving, easy-to-service modular construction, ASUS Chromebook C204 is ready for anything!
Ultimate rugged design
ASUS Chromebook C204 is built to withstand everyday classroom knocks, bumps, drops and spills without damage. Whether it is dropped from a desk or the dinner table the C204 is built like a tank and will keep on going.
Ready for action
Classrooms can be tough, but ASUS Chromebook C204 is tougher! Built to surpass demanding military-grade MIL-STD-810G durability standards, it's also torture-tested to pass stringent ASUS quality tests. It can withstand occasional drops of up to 120cm -more than standard desk height - and the hinge and I/O ports are fully tested to endure the stresses and strains of everyday use.
Ready, right out of the box
With your Chromebook's operation system - the Chrome OS, you can work smarter and more productively, with robust built-in security and automatic updates.
A little help on your Chromebook with the Google Assistant
Get more done fast with the Google Assistant on your ASUS Chromebook C204. Send an email, find documents, listen to music, access your calendar, or control smart home devices, all without switching screens. Just say "Hey Google" to get started.
All-day learning
With up to 12 hours battery life on a single charge, ASUS Chromebook C204 will last for a full day of classes and more. Students could enjoy continuous and uninterrupted learning without worry of battery life.
Thoughtful design for all ages
ASUS Chromebook C204 is not only rugged, but it's designed to be comfortable for everyone. The long key travel on the keyboard 1.5mm gives much better tactile feedback, for a more responsive and comfortable desktop-like typing experience. Working on the ASUS Chromebook C204 is a pleasure, not a chore.
Stress-free sharing
The 180° lay-flat hinge not only enables easier collaboration when you're in a group, but it also reduces stress on the mechanism too.
Good news for IT staff!
For easy on-site servicing and reduced downtime, ASUS Chromebook C204 has a modular construction that allows key components - such as the keyboard, battery, thermal module and motherboard - to be replaced in minutes using simple tools so that IT administrator could focus on the exact issues and send the device to the students in a short time.

Welcome to a new age of intelligence
ExpressConnect
New ExpressConnect automatically joins the strongest access point in the office and directs bandwidth to critical applications, wherever you work.
ExpressResponse
With Intel® Adaptix™ Technology, prioritize your most important apps, so they open faster and perform better.
ExpressSign-in
Get to work fast with our PC proximity sensor enabled by Intel® Context Sensing Technology that detects your presence to instantly wake and log you in via the IR camera and Windows Hello, all without lifting a finger. It locks when you walk away, so your work stays safer.
ExpressCharge

Choose from a 42WHr battery for lighter weight or a larger 63Whr battery for longer run time. Product Name: Galaxy Tab Active Pro SM-T547 Tablet
Description:
Samsung Galaxy Tab Active Pro SM-T547 Tablet - 10.1" Dual-core (2 Core) 2 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Storage - Android 9.0 Pie - 4G - Black - Qualcomm Snapdragon 670 SoC microSD Supported - 1920 x 1200 - LTE - 8 Megapixel Front Camera OCTACORE ANDROID UNLOCKED LTE BLACK
Stand up to real-world challenges with the Galaxy Tab Active Pro, a rugged tablet designed to withstand harsh conditions and equipped with the latest digital workflow tools to maximize your team's productivity. It's ideal for industries like asset management, retail, transportation, manufacturing, field service and public safety.
Features
Stand Up to Real-World Challenges
The Galaxy Tab Active Pro withstood 21 of the MIL-STD-810G tests so it's built to stand up to challenges the real world dishes out. Additionally, the Tab Active Pro and its S Pen have an IP68 rating giving them resistance to dust, dirt, sand, and water.
Get More Done, Effortlessly
The S Pen looks and feels like a typical pen but allows team members to easily jot down digital thoughts, sketch ideas or capture signatures without missing a beat. With the military-grade designed, IP68-rated Tab Active Pro and its IP68-rated S Pen, you can annotate in real time, edit with precision and work effectively no matter the condition.
Always Connected
Wireless data networks are now faster than ever, with LTE ensuring high-speed connectivity all the time. Always working, and always connected.
Always in its element
Tackle any situation easily with the field-ready 10.1" form factor of the Galaxy Tab Active Pro. Jot down worksite comments, view pictures in high resolution and review floor plans clearly and with ease. With Enhanced Touch, the Galaxy Tab Active Pro will react and operate in full capacity even with your gloves on in any environment.
Power for Hours
Your work doesn't stop-and neither does the Galaxy Tab Active Pro. With up to 15 hours on a full charge, you can create, edit and collaborate all day. Even when your battery runs low, you can still get the job done thanks to the simple and quick battery remove and replace functionality that lets you work uninterrupted.
Mobile Multi-tasking Has Never Been Easier With DeX
Samsung DeX creates a more productive, immersive PC-like experience, enabling businesses to be highly-productive outside the office and in tougher environments. Now, you can rely on one device for seamless transition and access to data anywhere-never missing a beat. Enhance the power of DeX with an eco-system of third party solution peripherals to further transform the Tab Active Pro into a powerful desktop-like experience. Start on your tablet, finish on your desktop.
Work That Doesn't Stop
The Galaxy Tab Active Pro's heavy-duty POGO Pin connector means rock-solid dependability. Charge and work seamlessly, with the POGO Pin that enables drop-in charging and accessory compatibility. Use it to quickly connect and charge or to easily attach a third party accessory.
Customize Your Quick Access
With the new programmable button, you can customize immediate access to your most critical Line of Business applications at the press of a button.

Description:
HPE 800W Flex Slot Platinum Hot Plug Low Halogen Power Supply Kit - 800 W - 230 V AC SPLY KIT PL-SI
How do you improve data center power efficiency without impacting IT performance? HPE Flexible Slot Power Supplies provide up to 96% power efficiency with 80Plus Titanium-certified power supplies that lower server power requirements and reduce power waste in your data center. This form factor is 25% smaller than previous generation power supplies, providing more space to add additional server options and improve the performance of your servers. These power supplies provide fast, tool-less hot plug access to server power supplies for greater serviceability and are supported across the entire HPE ProLiant Gen10 and HPE ProLiant 300 Series Gen9 Server families, simplifying your spares strategy and further reducing data center costs.

Description:
Dell Latitude 3000 3301 13.3" Notebook - 1920 x 1080 - Intel Core i5 (8th Gen) i5-8265U Quad-core (4 Core) 1.60 GHz - 8 GB RAM - 256 GB SSD - Windows 10 Pro - Intel UHD Graphics 620 - TrueLife - English Keyboard - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1DIMMS 256GB SS W10 13.3IN
Small in design. Big on collaboration.
Dell's smallest 13" essential business notebook features an innovative webcam for high-quality video conferencing and the latest Intel® processors.
Operating system
Available with Windows 10 Home or Windows 10 Pro - for a smooth, versatile PC experience.
Mobility with style
Lightweight: Travelling is easier than ever thanks to its compact design that fits perfectly into your carry-on, backpack or bag.

Minimize distractions: A 3-sided narrow border enhances your screen, so you can collaborate in online meetings or work on your latest projects in style. Upgrade to the Full HD display option to view your work with complete clarity.

Impressive inside and out: Available in aluminum or black, the sleek exterior outshines in any setting, while the diamond cut touch pad feels as good as it looks.

Redesigned hinge: Your laptop lifts slightly off the table when open past a 135-degree angle, allowing for improved air circulation and a more comfortable typing experience.

Intelligent thermals: The Latitude 3301 is smart enough to know when it's in your hands, lap or on a desk. This allows it to intelligently adapt its thermal profiles to stay cool. It remains cooler on your lap and full power is unleashed when stationary on a desk for maximum productivity.
Video conference from anywhere
Stay in focus: At just 2.7 mm, the new miniaturized webcam has a 4-element lens. It has more elements than typical webcams for sharp video in all areas of the frame.

Be seen in any light: By using advanced noise reduction, video quality is significantly improved, especially in dim lighting conditions.

Never miss a word: With Waves MaxxAudio® Pro, get an immersive audio experience that emulates an actual conference the an actual conference room, to hear and be heard for better collaboration. Now compatible with more accessories.

Remain powerful: The latest 8th generation Intel® up to 4-Core™ processor ensures apps run faster and large files are handled with ease.
Accelerate your workflow

Ready when you are: Turn on your computer by opening the lid with a new sensor. Then, log in instantly with the optional fingerprint reader integrated into the power button.

Power up: Keep the work flowing with a high-density battery and ExpressCharge, which allows an 80% charge in one hour.

Stay connected: Seamlessly work on the go thanks to optional mobile broadband supporting speeds up to 450Mbps.

Plug in: Quickly connect to peripherals with a full range of available ports, including USB Type-C™, Type-A and legacy ports like HDMI.

How do you improve data center power efficiency without impacting IT performance? HPE Flexible Slot Power Supplies provide up to 96% power efficiency with 80Plus Titanium-certified power supplies that lower server power requirements and reduce power waste in your data center. Description:
Lenovo 300e (2nd Gen) 82GK001PUS 11.6" Touchscreen Rugged 2 in 1 Notebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - AMD 3015e Dual-core (2 Core) 1.20 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Flash Memory - Black - AMD Chip - Windows 10 Pro - AMD Radeon Graphics - In-plane Switching (IPS) Technology - English Keyboard - 14.30 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 4GB 64GB 11.6IN W10P 64BIT
Features | The future of learning is here
Past meets future in the Lenovo 300e Gen 2, which combines the familiar Windows 10 Pro platform with the latest AMD processors. This 2 in 1 laptop has a 360-degree hinge allows students and teachers to transition seamlessly between four different modes for reading, writing, drawing, typing, content creation, and presentation.
Uninterrupted learning
In addition to a variety of ports, WiFi 6 capability, and a battery that lasts all day, the 300e Gen 2 laptop features a 720p front-facing and optional 5MP world-facing camera that turns any classroom into an interactive learning environment. This ensures that class continues as scheduled even if students and teachers are connecting from home.
Smart. Like your students.
Tap, scroll, and swipe with a finger on the 300e Gen 2 laptop's 11 inch, 10-point multitouch display. Or use a common No. 2 pencil to interact directly and safely with the screen without fear of scratches. This Pencil Touch technology is ideal for taking tests, drawing, and notetaking because it's more accurate than using a finger. When even more precision is required, an optional integrated AES pen is located inside of a small port.
Security isn't a problem
The 300e Gen 2 laptop is protected by multiple built-in security solutions from Windows 10 Pro. Additionally, this device comes with a Kensington lock slot that gives you the option of locking it to a desk to prevent physical theft.
Tough tech
The 300e Gen 2 AMD 2 in 1 laptop is designed to withstand the scrapes, slips, and spills of a typical school day-whether in the classroom or at the kitchen table-with a drop-resistant design, up to 29.5" (75cm), roughly the height of a school desk. It also has a water-resistant (up to 330 ml / 11 oz) keyboard and reinforced 360-degree Sync Hinge.
Light your load
With up to 14.3 hours of battery life, the 300e Gen 2 laptop lasts an entire school day and then some, no need to haul power cords and adapters around. Students can work a full day and take the laptop home to recharge overnight for the next day's classes.
So productive, it almost does your homework
With its AMD processor, the Lenovo 100e 2nd Gen AMD laptop seamlessly runs Windows 10 and apps from the Microsoft Store. Choose from thousands of education apps, like Office 365, Microsoft Teams, OneNote Class Notebook, Minecraft Education Edition, Kahoot!, GeoGebra, and more. Easily work with multiple windows and browser tabs open at the same time.

Description:
Lenovo 300e (2nd Gen) 82GK001PUS 11.6" Touchscreen Rugged 2 in 1 Notebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - AMD 3015e Dual-core (2 Core) 1.20 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Flash Memory - Black - AMD Chip - Windows 10 Pro - AMD Radeon Graphics - In-plane Switching (IPS) Technology - English Keyboard - 14.30 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 4GB 64GB 11.6IN W10P 64BIT
Features | The future of learning is here
Past meets future in the Lenovo 300e Gen 2, which combines the familiar Windows 10 Pro platform with the latest AMD processors. This 2 in 1 laptop has a 360-degree hinge allows students and teachers to transition seamlessly between four different modes for reading, writing, drawing, typing, content creation, and presentation.
Uninterrupted learning
In addition to a variety of ports, WiFi 6 capability, and a battery that lasts all day, the 300e Gen 2 laptop features a 720p front-facing and optional 5MP world-facing camera that turns any classroom into an interactive learning environment. This ensures that class continues as scheduled even if students and teachers are connecting from home.
Smart. Like your students.
Tap, scroll, and swipe with a finger on the 300e Gen 2 laptop's 11 inch, 10-point multitouch display. Or use a common No. 2 pencil to interact directly and safely with the screen without fear of scratches. This Pencil Touch technology is ideal for taking tests, drawing, and notetaking because it's more accurate than using a finger. When even more precision is required, an optional integrated AES pen is located inside of a small port.
Security isn't a problem
The 300e Gen 2 laptop is protected by multiple built-in security solutions from Windows 10 Pro. Additionally, this device comes with a Kensington lock slot that gives you the option of locking it to a desk to prevent physical theft.
Tough tech
The 300e Gen 2 AMD 2 in 1 laptop is designed to withstand the scrapes, slips, and spills of a typical school day-whether in the classroom or at the kitchen table-with a drop-resistant design, up to 29.5" (75cm), roughly the height of a school desk. It also has a water-resistant (up to 330 ml / 11 oz) keyboard and reinforced 360-degree Sync Hinge.
Light your load
With up to 14.3 hours of battery life, the 300e Gen 2 laptop lasts an entire school day and then some, no need to haul power cords and adapters around. Students can work a full day and take the laptop home to recharge overnight for the next day's classes.
So productive, it almost does your homework
With its AMD processor, the Lenovo 100e 2nd Gen AMD laptop seamlessly runs Windows 10 and apps from the Microsoft Store. Choose from thousands of education apps, like Office 365, Microsoft Teams, OneNote Class Notebook, Minecraft Education Edition, Kahoot!, GeoGebra, and more. Easily work with multiple windows and browser tabs open at the same time.

HPE SmartMemory 32GB DDR4 SDRAM Memory Module - 32 GB (1 x 32GB) - DDR4-2666/PC4-21300 DDR4 SDRAM - 2666 MHz - CL19 - 1.20 V - ECC - Registered - 288-pin - RDIMM NO DEAL REG PRICING PL-SI
Has your server been configured with the memory required to perform as its role expands over time? HPE Server Memory is designed for SMB and enterprise customers with a significant need for performance and capacity along with a desire to manage TCO. HPE SmartMemory offers the widest selection of memory types and capacities, enabling total server memory optimization, runs at top throughput speed and is amongst the most power-efficient memory available. In addition to performance and efficiency, HPE SmartMemory also delivers on reliability. Only the highest-quality DRAM modules are selected from top suppliers. Now more than ever, DRAM quality is critical, as data center trends such as server virtualization, cloud computing, and the use of large database applications, have increased the need for higher-capacity memory with greater uptime. HPE SmartMemory undergoes rigorous qualification and testing processes that unlock memory performance features available only with HPE Servers.
What's new
Features
High Performance
HPE DDR4 2666 MT/s server memory provides up to a 66% improvement in bandwidth at DDR4-2666 MT/s in comparison to DDR4 2400 MT/s memory modules.
Delivers up to a 4.7% improvement in latency at DDR4-2666 MT/ s in comparison to DDR4 2400 MT/s memory modules.
High Reliability
HPE DDR4 SmartMemory modules have been tested and qualified on all Hewlett Packard Enterprise server platforms to deliver the highest level of signal integrity.
Prevents unnecessary DIMM replacement and reduces server downtime with advanced memory error detection technology.
Hewlett Packard Enterprise server memory is made of the highest quality materials, reducing issues that may affect signal integrity, increasing system reliability.
Hewlett Packard Enterprise server memory speed targets provide customers with memory that performs above industry standards, allowing them to increase performance without having to increase the amount of memory purchased.

Description:
HPE SmartMemory 32GB DDR4 SDRAM Memory Module - 32 GB (1 x 32GB) - DDR4-2666/PC4-21300 DDR4 SDRAM - 2666 MHz - CL19 - 1.20 V - ECC - Registered - 288-pin - RDIMM NO DEAL REG PRICING PL-SI
Has your server been configured with the memory required to perform as its role expands over time? HPE Server Memory is designed for SMB and enterprise customers with a significant need for performance and capacity along with a desire to manage TCO. HPE SmartMemory offers the widest selection of memory types and capacities, enabling total server memory optimization, runs at top throughput speed and is amongst the most power-efficient memory available. In addition to performance and efficiency, HPE SmartMemory also delivers on reliability. Only the highest-quality DRAM modules are selected from top suppliers. Now more than ever, DRAM quality is critical, as data center trends such as server virtualization, cloud computing, and the use of large database applications, have increased the need for higher-capacity memory with greater uptime. HPE SmartMemory undergoes rigorous qualification and testing processes that unlock memory performance features available only with HPE Servers.
What's new
Features
High Performance
HPE DDR4 2666 MT/s server memory provides up to a 66% improvement in bandwidth at DDR4-2666 MT/s in comparison to DDR4 2400 MT/s memory modules.
Delivers up to a 4.7% improvement in latency at DDR4-2666 MT/ s in comparison to DDR4 2400 MT/s memory modules.
High Reliability
HPE DDR4 SmartMemory modules have been tested and qualified on all Hewlett Packard Enterprise server platforms to deliver the highest level of signal integrity.
Prevents unnecessary DIMM replacement and reduces server downtime with advanced memory error detection technology.
Hewlett Packard Enterprise server memory is made of the highest quality materials, reducing issues that may affect signal integrity, increasing system reliability.
Hewlett Packard Enterprise server memory speed targets provide customers with memory that performs above industry standards, allowing them to increase performance without having to increase the amount of memory purchased.

Samsung Chromebook Plus XE525QBB-K01US LTE 12.2" Touchscreen 2 in 1 Chromebook - 1920 x 1200 - Intel Celeron 3965Y 1.50 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Stealth Silver - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics 615 - 8.10 Hour Battery Run Time - 4G - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 360-DEGREE HINGE/32GB/STEALTH
Get the bigger picture
Introducing the Samsung Chromebook Plus V2 (LTE)
With built-in LTE, the lightweight 2-in-1 Chromebook Plus lets you get more done anywhere, anytime, without having to search for Wi-Fi. Stay on top of projects with the included pen, dual camera, and full Google experience. Cross more off your list without slowing down with a powerful battery and Intel® processor.
From laptop to tablet to sketchbook and more
Weighing slightly over 3 pounds, the Chromebook Plus is light enough to slip into your bag and take anywhere. Easily fold it into tablet mode to switch between typing and writing down ideas.
Always connected
No Wi-Fi? No problem, thanks to LTE. Access the cloud and Google Apps anytime, anywhere. Instantly upload photos and videos to social media, or chat with loved ones via Hangouts.
The power of the pen
Experience the power of the precise built-in pen that's ready when you need it and never needs charging. Write a note, sketch an idea, edit a document, magnify and take screenshots.
Two cameras, unlimited views
Change your perspective with the 13MP world-facing camera with autofocus. Fold your laptop into tablet mode and capture your view from any angle or zoom in to take photos. Use the front camera to video chat. Store photos and videos right on your cloud.
Get the most out of Google
Take your experiences to the big screen. Navigate intuitively with the keyboard and touchpad. Easily download your favorite apps, movies and games from Google Play.
Do more. Store more.
Tackle anything with a long-lasting battery and an Intel® Celeron® processor that lets you work on multiple things at once. Store more with 32GB of built-in memory and expand your storage with a microSD card.

Welcome to a new age of intelligence
ExpressConnect

ExpressResponse
With Intel® Adaptix™ Technology, prioritize your most important apps, so they open faster and perform better.
ExpressSign-in
Get to work fast with our PC proximity sensor enabled by Intel® Context Sensing Technology that detects your presence to instantly wake and log you in via the IR camera and Windows Hello, all without lifting a finger. It locks when you walk away, so your work stays safer.
ExpressCharge

Intelligent Audio
Collaborate like you're in the same room. Intelligent Audio enhances your audio quality and reduces background noises, so you can hear and be heard, creating a better conference experience for all.
Fully loaded and ready to work
Take charge: Keep working with outstanding battery life plus intelligent settings to preserve power when you're running low. Choose from a 42WHr battery for lighter weight or a larger 63Whr battery for longer run time. Get longer battery life when you choose the Super Low Power panel, which consumes less power than a standard display without impacting the brightness of the screen.

According to research, 1 out of every 4 users would question their job and the company they work for if they had a negative experience with their technology.
Dell Technologies Unified Workspace is transforming the employee experience and ensuring IT has proactive, predictive and automated solutions to deliver on the promise of a modern workday, while simplifying their ability to deploy, secure, manage and support their environment.

Deploy: ProDeploy in the Unified Workspace allows IT to move away from traditional, high-touch, manual deployment, and instead, ship devices preconfigured with company apps and settings from the Dell factory directly to their end users-having end users up and working on day one.

Secure: Dell Trusted Devices provide a foundation to a modern workforce environment with invisible and seamless protection to ensure smarter, faster experiences. End users stay productive and IT stays confident with modern security solutions for the Dell Trusted Device.

Manage: Dell Client Command Suite + VMware Workspace ONE offers integrated capabilities that deliver a unified endpoint management experience for IT, enabling them to manage firmware, OS, and apps from one console, while also creating seamless experiences for end users.

Support: ProSupport resolves hardware issues up to 11x faster than the competition. ProSupport for PCs offers 24x7 access to in-region ProSupport engineers who contact IT when critical issues arise, so you can focus on what's next, not what just happened.

ProSupport Plus helps IT stay a step ahead and virtually eliminate unplanned downtime due to hardware issues. You get all the capabilities of ProSupport, as well as AI-driven alerts to prevent failures and repairs for accidents.

ExpressConnect

ExpressResponse

HPE SmartMemory 16GB DDR4 SDRAM Memory Module - 16 GB (1 x 16GB) - DDR4-2666/PC4-21300 DDR4 SDRAM - 2666 MHz - CL19 - 1.20 V - ECC - Registered - 288-pin - DIMM KIT NO DEAL REG
Has your server been configured with the memory required to perform as its role expands over time? HPE Server Memory is designed for SMB and enterprise customers with a significant need for performance and capacity along with a desire to manage TCO. HPE SmartMemory offers the widest selection of memory types and capacities, enabling total server memory optimization, runs at top throughput speed and is amongst the most power-efficient memory available. In addition to performance and efficiency, HPE SmartMemory also delivers on reliability. Only the highest-quality DRAM modules are selected from top suppliers. Now more than ever, DRAM quality is critical, as data center trends such as server virtualization, cloud computing, and the use of large database applications, have increased the need for higher-capacity memory with greater uptime. HPE SmartMemory undergoes rigorous qualification and testing processes that unlock memory performance features available only with HPE Servers.
What's new
Features
High Performance
HPE DDR4 2666 MT/s server memory provides up to a 66% improvement in bandwidth at DDR4-2666 MT/s in comparison to DDR4 2400 MT/s memory modules.
Delivers up to a 4.7% improvement in latency at DDR4-2666 MT/ s in comparison to DDR4 2400 MT/s memory modules.
High Reliability
HPE DDR4 SmartMemory modules have been tested and qualified on all Hewlett Packard Enterprise server platforms to deliver the highest level of signal integrity.
Prevents unnecessary DIMM replacement and reduces server downtime with advanced memory error detection technology.
Hewlett Packard Enterprise server memory is made of the highest quality materials, reducing issues that may affect signal integrity, increasing system reliability.
Hewlett Packard Enterprise server memory speed targets provide customers with memory that performs above industry standards, allowing them to increase performance without having to increase the amount of memory purchased.

Dell OptiPlex 3000 3080 Desktop Computer - Intel Core i3 10th Gen I3-10105T Quad-core (4 Core) 3 GHz - 4 GB RAM DDR4 SDRAM - 500 GB HDD - Micro PC - Black - Windows 10 Pro 64-bit - Intel DDR4 SDRAM - English Keyboard - 65 W 4GB 500GB 7.2K W10
Essential, compact desktop.
Essential commercial micro form factor desktop that delivers best-in-class security and performance with 10th Gen Intel® processors.
Operating System
Available with Windows 10 Pro - for a smooth, versatile PC experience.
Work smart
Flexible mounting: With multiple mounting options, the 3080 micro fits exactly where you need it to.

Simple to maintain: The 3080 micro delivers easier access to parts without needing to remove the front bezel.

Work confidently: Built secure with TPM 2.0, standard security lock slot, padlock loop, intrusion switch, and SED hard drive.

Stay Cool: Utilizing the new cooling design of the front bezel, the 3080 micro maximizes air intake to keep your system temperature down.
Uncompromising productivity
Power through your work: Built with up to 10th Generation Intel® Celeron, Pentium, Core™ i3 or i5 processors for faster performance.

Optimized chassis design: The 3000 series now has simplified configurations to be more cost effective and provide an easier purchasing decision.
Intelligence built in. Modernization built on.
We know that having the right device is just the start to a great workday. Employees need intelligent, intuitive and responsive experiences that allow them to work productively and without interruption. According to research, 1 out of every 4 users would question their job and the company they work for if they had a negative experience with their technology.

Dell Technologies Unified Workspace is transforming the employee experience and ensuring IT has proactive, predictive and automated solutions to deliver on the promise of a modern workday, while simplifying their ability to deploy, secure, manage and support their environment.

Deploy: ProDeploy in the Unified Workspace allows IT to move away from traditional, high-touch, manual deployment, and instead, ship devices preconfigured with company apps and settings from the Dell factory directly to their end users-having end users up and working on day one.

Secure: Dell Trusted Devices provide a foundation to a modern workforce environment with invisible and seamless protection to ensure smarter, faster experiences. End users stay productive and IT stays confident with modern security solutions for the Dell Trusted Device.

Manage: Dell Client Command Suite + VMware Workspace ONE offers integrated capabilities that deliver a unified endpoint management experience for IT, enabling them to manage firmware, OS, and apps from one console, while also creating seamless experiences for end users.

Support: ProSupport resolves hardware issues up to 11x faster than the competition. ProSupport for PCs offers 24x7 access to in-region ProSupport engineers who contact IT when critical issues arise, so you can focus on what's next, not what just happened.

ProSupport Plus helps IT stay a step ahead and virtually eliminate unplanned downtime due to hardware issues. You get all the capabilities of ProSupport, as well as AI-driven alerts to prevent failures and repairs for accidents.

Description:
Dell Chromebook 11 3000 3100 11.6" Touchscreen 2 in 1 Chromebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - Intel Celeron N4020 Dual-core (2 Core) 1.10 GHz - 8 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Black - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics - English Keyboard - 13 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1DIMMS 32GB TOUCH 1366X768 3C
Learning without boundaries
An 11-inch 2-in-1 with best-in-class durability and up to 13 hours of battery life empowers students to learn and collaborate.
Operating System
Operating system - Google Chrome OS
Designed to last beyond the bell
The Chromebook 3000 Series is rigorously tested to endure the school day and beyond. Students can learn uninterrupted with tamper- and spill-resistant keyboards and a long battery life.
Tested to endure the school day

Uncompromised durability: Rigorously tested beyond MIL-STD standards, the Chromebook 3100 2-in-1 keeps up with the entire school day and then some. It's tested to survive 5,000 free fall micro-drops and 30-inch drops onto steel, while rubberized edges minimize impacts from drops and bumps.

Survives spills: Students can learn, discover and share without worry thanks to the spill- and tamper-resistant keyboard that withstands up to 12 ounces of liquid. Plus, its top mounted design ensures the entire palm rest doesn't need to be replaced in case of damage to the keyboard.

Protected ports: Ports are covered and secured with reinforced brackets, and they're tested to ensure students can connect and disconnect as many times as they need.
Enabling learning anytime, anywhere
Group learning made easy: The Chromebook 3100 2-in-1 is designed for interactive learning. It supports up to four modes (flat, tent, tablet or laptop) for viewing and collaborating, while the available world facing camera allows students to take advantage of flipped viewing and recording angles.

Good past the last bell: With up to 13 hours of battery life, this trusty 2-in-1 gets kids through even the longest school days. The USB Type-C™ port supports power and data transfers to keep students connected.

Powerful performance: The Intel® Dual Core™ Celeron processor provides robust performance and power. And because it boots in less than 10 seconds, students are ready to learn at a moment's notice.

Tougher screens: Corning® Gorilla® Glass NBT™ on the touch displays delivers eight to 10 times higher scratch resistance.
One cart to charge them all

The Dell Compact Charging Cart comes with a space saving design, making it easy to charge and store up to 36 systems at once.
Our job is to make yours easier
Google gives you more: Add the optional Chromebook G Suite for Education for a wealth of Google apps for students and teachers, including Classroom. This core feature keeps students organized and in touch and allows teachers to create, distribute and grade assignments simply and in one place.

Compact. Connected. Cinematic.
Go anywhere and stay connected with 4G LTE on the Galaxy Tab A (8.4" , 2020). With a long-lasting battery, you can stream your favorite music, shows and movies for over 10 hours on a single charge. Whether you're traveling, unwinding or enjoying a quick break, Galaxy Tab A's compact, slim design and vivid display make it the perfect companion. Head out, and stay connected without Wi-Fi.
No Wi-Fi needed.
Simply add the Galaxy Tab A to your existing data plan, and you're ready to use it anywhere. 4G LTE connectivity lets you browse your favorite websites and streaming platforms, no Wi-Fi needed.
Perfectly portable.
The Galaxy Tab A gives you more room to view your favorite content on its expansive display. The premium finish and lightweight design make it easy to use at home and on the go.
Entertainment Ready.
Experience entertainment on a vivid, crystal clear display paired with dual speakers for spacious surround sound.
Binge-ready battery.
Long-lasting battery gives you 10 hours of use, while its Fast-Charging USB-C port allows you to quickly recharge.
Room for everything.
Store it all with built-in 32GB internal memory. Expand up to an additional 512GB with a microSD card1 at any time.
Connect and capture.
Video chat with friends and family on the 5MP front-facing camera. The 8MP rear camera is equipped with autofocus-ideal for recording, capturing and sharing everything.

There's nothing mainstream about it
This smaller, sleeker 14-inch laptop lets you get to work faster than ever thanks to its scalable design and powerful performance.
Operating System
Available with Windows 10 Pro - for a smooth, versatile PC experience.
Welcome to a new age of intelligence
ExpressConnect
New ExpressConnect automatically joins the strongest access point in the office and directs bandwidth to critical applications, wherever you work.
ExpressResponse
With Intel® Adaptix™ Technology, prioritize your most important apps, so they open faster and perform better.
ExpressSign-in
Get to work fast with our PC proximity sensor enabled by Intel® Context Sensing Technology that detects your presence to instantly wake and log you in via the IR camera and Windows Hello, all without lifting a finger. It locks when you walk away, so your work stays safer.
ExpressCharge
Dell Optimizer extends runtime and improves battery performance by adapting to your patterns. ExpressCharge Boost delivers up to 35% charge in about 20 minutes, or up to 80% charge in an hour with ExpressCharge.
Intelligent Audio
Collaborate like you're in the same room. Intelligent Audio enhances your audio quality and reduces background noises, so you can hear and be heard, creating a better conference experience for all.
Fully loaded and ready to work
Take charge: Keep working with outstanding battery life plus intelligent settings to preserve power when you're running low. Choose from a 42WHr battery for lighter weight or a larger 63Whr battery for longer run time. Get longer battery life when you choose the Super Low Power panel, which consumes less power than a standard display without impacting the brightness of the screen.

Intelligent Audio
Collaborate like you're in the same room. Intelligent Audio enhances your audio quality and reduces background noises, so you can hear and be heard, creating a better conference experience for all.
Take the conference with you
Transform every room: Make every call feel like you're there with premium built-in speakerphone and Intelligent Audio, which adapts to your surroundings to reduce echoes and background noises.

Product Name: Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller
Description:
HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller - 12Gb/s SAS, Serial ATA/600 - PCI Express 3.0 x8 - Plug-in Module - RAID Supported - 0, 1, 5, 10 RAID Level - 2 - 8 Total SAS Port(s) - 8 SAS Port(s) Internal - Linux, PC - 0 Byte CTRLR PL=SI
Are you looking for a cost effective, enterprise-class controller for internal attached drives without occupying a PCIe expansion slot? The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller, supporting 12 Gb/s SAS and PCIe 3.0, provides a cost-effective storage solution with enterprise-class reliability supporting RAID 0, 1, 5, and 10 and software-defined storage (SDS). This controller has eight internal SAS lanes, allowing connection to SAS or SATA drives, supports Mixed Mode operations of RAID and HBA simultaneously, and offers encryption for data-at rest on any drive. This type-a modular controller occupies a dedicated storage slot without occupying a PCIe expansion slot.
Cost-Effective SAS Storage Connectivity
The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller is a cost effective enterprise-class controller that provides the basic building blocks for simple RAID storage solutions while delivering 12 Gb/s SAS connectivity on HPE ProLiant Gen10 Servers when connected to 12 Gb/s internal storage devices.
Offers a low-cost solution to enable software-defined storage.
Built-in Reliability and Security
The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller protects data-at-rest on any drive attached to the controller with HPE Smart Array SR Secure Encryption (optional license).
Comply with regulations for sensitive data, such as HIPAA and Sarbanes-Oxley with HPE Smart Array SR Secure Encryption.
Preserve data integrity with HPE SmartSSD Wear Gauge, which alerts you to potential drive issues before a drive fails.
Improved Efficiency and Storage Management
The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller has increased flexibility with Mixed Mode which operates in RAID and HBA simultaneously and eliminates the expense of having to purchase another controller.
Rapidly configure simple RAID volumes on servers with the UEFI storage configuration tool, which also facilitates scripting support to configure an array via iLO through RESTful interface.
Quickly set up, configure, and manage drives attached to the controller with HPE Smart Storage Administrator (SSA), an intuitive interface used to create RAID volumes, manage advanced controller features, and deploy Smart Array solutions.

Product Description
ASUS Chromebook C403 combines big-screen productivity with classroom-ready toughness. Its large 14-inch display and ergonomic keyboard let you get things done in total comfort, and its rugged construction makes it a laptop you can rely on, whether you're using it for school, or sharing screens with teachers or family. It's packed with ruggedized features such as the all-round rubber bumper, spill-resistant keyboard and ultratough hinge. With its easy-to-service modular design and long-lasting battery, ASUS Chromebook C403 is the smartest choice for learning!
Military-Grade Durability
To protect your investment, it is built to surpass demanding military-grade MIL-STD-810G durability standards. It can withstand occasional drops of up to 3.9 feet and the hinge and I/O ports are fully tested to endure the stresses and strains of everyday use.
Easy to maintain
Reduce downtime with A modular construction that allows key components - such as the keyboard, battery, thermal module and motherboard - to be replaced in minutes using simple tools.
Spill-resistant keyboard
Accidents happen, and ASUS Chromebook C403 is ready for them: its spill-resistant keyboard can cope with liquid spills of up to 66cc without harm, so minor splashes on the desk or dinner table can be easily drained, cleaned, and dried.
Durable 3D-textured finish
ASUS Chromebook C403 keeps its smart looks for longer, with a tough micro-dimpled finish that means no more worries about minor scratches or fingerprints!
Full port support
Full connectivity is vital when you want to get things done. In addition to Wi-Fi and Bluetooth 4.2, the ASUS C403 gives you two USB Type-C (Gen 1) and two USB Type-A (Gen 1) and a microSD card reader.
180 degree hinge
The 180° lay-flat hinge not only enables easier collaboration when you're in a group, but it also reduces stress on the mechanism too.
Chrome OS
With Chromebook's operating system - the Chrome OS, you can work smarter and more productively, with robust built-in security and automatic updates. In addition you can explore a vast world of apps with the Google Play Store. Google Play and the Google Play logo are trademarks of Google LLC.

Product Name: Chromebook Flip C434 C434TA-DSM4T 14" Touchscreen Chromebook
Description:
Asus Chromebook Flip C434 C434TA-DSM4T 14" Touchscreen Chromebook - Full HD - 1920 x 1080 - Intel Core M (8th Gen) m3-8100Y Dual-core (2 Core) 1.10 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Flash Memory - Black, Silver - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics 615 - 10 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1.1 GHZ 4GB 64GB TOUCH SCREEN
The Best Just Got Better

The stunning new ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 takes convertible Chromebook design to the next level. Its stylish contemporary looks, compact portability and powerful specifications are all designed to let you get things done with no fuss, all day and every day. ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 features a new four-sided NanoEdge 14-inch display - with ultraslim bezels and an incredible 87% screen-to-body ratio - for a truly immersive viewing experience, and the unique 360° ErgoLift hinge lets you work in supreme comfort. There's a world of apps to explore on the Google Play Store. When only the best is good enough, ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 delivers.

CRAFTSMANSHIP
Crafted to perfection
ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 is styled for today, with a precision-crafted all-aluminum chassis finished with elegant diamond-cut anodized edges. Its refined looks are the perfect match for those who appreciate on-the-go versatility combined with peerless design.
MOBILITY
The 13" laptop with a 14" display
ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 is not only slim and light, but the new NanoEdge design gives it an ultracompact footprint, so you can enjoy all the benefits of a 14-inch FHD display in a chassis that's as small as many 13-inch laptops.
NANOEDGE DISPLAY
Unbounded vision with the NanoEdge display
Designed to give you the most screen area in the least physical space, the new four-sided NanoEdge display is simply breathtaking: it makes any visuals more immersive, with less distraction for your eyes. The ultraslim bezels are just 5mm thin at the sides for a near-borderless experience, and the crisp, clear, high-resolution screen gives you a beautiful creative workplace.
HINGE
Precision-engineered versatility
Featuring a precision-engineered mechanism, the versatile 360° ErgoLift hinge on ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 has a silky-smooth action that holds the display securely at any angle. This innovative hinge has a dual action that lifts and tilts the keyboard into the perfect typing position when the display is rotated into laptop mode. It also helps enhance the powerful audio, by creating extra space underneath the laptop.
PERFORMANCE
Breeze through your tasks all day long
Featuring powerful latest Intel® processors, ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 delivers great performance for popular apps, with extraordinary battery life. Combined with the full power of G Suite and other productivity apps from the Google Play store, ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 lets you breeze through all your everyday tasks on the go. The power-efficient ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 is designed to last for up to 10 hours on a single charge, so you can work or play throughout the day while you're on the move.
CONNECTIVITY
USB-C for ultimate flexibility
Two full-function reversible USB 3.1 Gen 1 Type-C™ (USB-C™) ports make it easy to charge your ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 or connect it to devices and external displays. For maximum convenience and compatibility, there's also a standard USB 3.1 Gen 1 Type-A port, and a microSD slot makes it easy to add extra storage.
WI-FI
Faster, more stable Wi-Fi connections
ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 includes dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi for strong, stable signals and fast data-transmission speeds. As an added advantage, 802.11ac Wi-Fi is less prone to interference from other wireless devices operating on the same frequency band.

Product Name: Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller
Description:
HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller - 12Gb/s SAS, Serial ATA/600 - PCI Express 3.0 x8 - Plug-in Module - RAID Supported - 0, 1, 5, 10 RAID Level - 2 - 8 Total SAS Port(s) - 8 SAS Port(s) Internal - Linux, PC - 0 Byte CTRLR PL=SI
Are you looking for a cost effective, enterprise-class controller for internal attached drives without occupying a PCIe expansion slot? The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller, supporting 12 Gb/s SAS and PCIe 3.0, provides a cost-effective storage solution with enterprise-class reliability supporting RAID 0, 1, 5, and 10 and software-defined storage (SDS). This controller has eight internal SAS lanes, allowing connection to SAS or SATA drives, supports Mixed Mode operations of RAID and HBA simultaneously, and offers encryption for data-at rest on any drive. This type-a modular controller occupies a dedicated storage slot without occupying a PCIe expansion slot.
Cost-Effective SAS Storage Connectivity
The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller is a cost effective enterprise-class controller that provides the basic building blocks for simple RAID storage solutions while delivering 12 Gb/s SAS connectivity on HPE ProLiant Gen10 Servers when connected to 12 Gb/s internal storage devices.
Offers a low-cost solution to enable software-defined storage.
Built-in Reliability and Security
The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller protects data-at-rest on any drive attached to the controller with HPE Smart Array SR Secure Encryption (optional license).
Comply with regulations for sensitive data, such as HIPAA and Sarbanes-Oxley with HPE Smart Array SR Secure Encryption.
Preserve data integrity with HPE SmartSSD Wear Gauge, which alerts you to potential drive issues before a drive fails.
Improved Efficiency and Storage Management
The HPE Smart Array E208i-a SR Gen10 Controller has increased flexibility with Mixed Mode which operates in RAID and HBA simultaneously and eliminates the expense of having to purchase another controller.
Rapidly configure simple RAID volumes on servers with the UEFI storage configuration tool, which also facilitates scripting support to configure an array via iLO through RESTful interface.
Quickly set up, configure, and manage drives attached to the controller with HPE Smart Storage Administrator (SSA), an intuitive interface used to create RAID volumes, manage advanced controller features, and deploy Smart Array solutions.

Asus Chromebook C403 C403NA-YH02-BL 14" Rugged Chromebook - HD - 1366 x 768 - Intel Celeron N3350 Dual-core (2 Core) 1.10 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 32 GB Flash Memory - Dark Blue - Intel Chip - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics - 10 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1.1 GHZ 4GB 32GB NO TOUCH SCREEN
Product Description
ASUS Chromebook C403 combines big-screen productivity with classroom-ready toughness. Its large 14-inch display and ergonomic keyboard let you get things done in total comfort, and its rugged construction makes it a laptop you can rely on, whether you're using it for school, or sharing screens with teachers or family. It's packed with ruggedized features such as the all-round rubber bumper, spill-resistant keyboard and ultratough hinge. With its easy-to-service modular design and long-lasting battery, ASUS Chromebook C403 is the smartest choice for learning!
Military-Grade Durability
To protect your investment, it is built to surpass demanding military-grade MIL-STD-810G durability standards. It can withstand occasional drops of up to 3.9 feet and the hinge and I/O ports are fully tested to endure the stresses and strains of everyday use.
Easy to maintain
Reduce downtime with A modular construction that allows key components - such as the keyboard, battery, thermal module and motherboard - to be replaced in minutes using simple tools.
Spill-resistant keyboard
Accidents happen, and ASUS Chromebook C403 is ready for them: its spill-resistant keyboard can cope with liquid spills of up to 66cc without harm, so minor splashes on the desk or dinner table can be easily drained, cleaned, and dried.
Durable 3D-textured finish
ASUS Chromebook C403 keeps its smart looks for longer, with a tough micro-dimpled finish that means no more worries about minor scratches or fingerprints!
Full port support
Full connectivity is vital when you want to get things done. In addition to Wi-Fi and Bluetooth 4.2, the ASUS C403 gives you two USB Type-C (Gen 1) and two USB Type-A (Gen 1) and a microSD card reader.
180 degree hinge
The 180° lay-flat hinge not only enables easier collaboration when you're in a group, but it also reduces stress on the mechanism too.
Chrome OS
With Chromebook's operating system - the Chrome OS, you can work smarter and more productively, with robust built-in security and automatic updates. In addition you can explore a vast world of apps with the Google Play Store. Google Play and the Google Play logo are trademarks of Google LLC.

Samsung Galaxy Chromebook 2 XE530QDA-KB2US 13.3" Touchscreen 2 in 1 Chromebook - Full HD - 1920 x 1080 - Intel Celeron 5205U 1.90 GHz - 4 GB RAM - Mercury Gray - Intel SoC - Chrome OS - Intel UHD Graphics - 13 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ax Wireless LAN Standard FHD QLED MERCURY GRAY 5205U
Work-life balance has never been better, thanks to the world's first QLED Chromebook. Dive into your favorite pastimes or present your next big idea with a larger-than-life, vibrant color display. With the power and speed of 10th Gen Intel® Core™ processing, the Galaxy Chromebook 2 is ready to take your goals to the next level whether you are an early morning go-getter or a late-night studier. Plus, thanks to a sleek, compact design, and a battery that works around the clock-it's simple to see Galaxy Chromebook 2 has everything you need to do more in the moment, and still stay connected to what matters most.
Leading at CES
Awarded Best Chromebook by CNN Underscored, the world's first QLED Chromebook impressed at CES. Whether you're an early morning go-getter or late-night studier, see how the Galaxy Chromebook 2 can take your goals to the next level.
See your best ideas in true QLED color
Get awestruck by every image with the world's first jaw-dropping QLED Galaxy Chromebook 2, that produces over a 100% volume.
The power and speed you deserve
Whether your working, studying or relaxing, Galaxy Chromebook 2 has you covered. With the latest Intel Core processor, you'll get super-fast speeds. Plus, Wi-Fi 6 GIG+ that's up to 3x faster than standard Wi-Fi gives you a super smooth performance.
Sound that puts you in every frame
Smart Amp audio surrounds you in sound up to 178% more powerful than normal amps, so you can leave the outside world behind.
Sleek design made to stand out
Featuring an ultra-thin design and eye-catching Fiesta Red color, the Galaxy Chromebook 2 is compact and ready for impact.With technology as slim, sleek and savvy as this, it's no wonder they're staring.
A battery that's above and beyond
Stay dialed in on-the-go with an all-day battery that keeps up no matter how many checkmarks your to-do list demands.
Inspiration at your fingertips
When inspiration strikes, you're prepared. Add any USI pen to your Galaxy Chromebook 2 and enjoy industry-leading pressure sensitivity whether you're writing your boss an email, or creating boss-level original content.
Personal assistant included
Now you can tell your Galaxy Chromebook 2 to do something simply by talking to it. With just one word, Google Assistant is here to support you and all your commands.

Product Name: Chromebook Flip C434 C434TA-DSM4T 14" Touchscreen Chromebook
Description:
Asus Chromebook Flip C434 C434TA-DSM4T 14" Touchscreen Chromebook - Full HD - 1920 x 1080 - Intel Core M (8th Gen) m3-8100Y Dual-core (2 Core) 1.10 GHz - 4 GB RAM - 64 GB Flash Memory - Black, Silver - Chrome OS - Intel HD Graphics 615 - 10 Hour Battery Run Time - IEEE 802.11ac Wireless LAN Standard 1.1 GHZ 4GB 64GB TOUCH SCREEN
The Best Just Got Better

The stunning new ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 takes convertible Chromebook design to the next level. Its stylish contemporary looks, compact portability and powerful specifications are all designed to let you get things done with no fuss, all day and every day. ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 features a new four-sided NanoEdge 14-inch display - with ultraslim bezels and an incredible 87% screen-to-body ratio - for a truly immersive viewing experience, and the unique 360° ErgoLift hinge lets you work in supreme comfort. There's a world of apps to explore on the Google Play Store. When only the best is good enough, ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 delivers.

CRAFTSMANSHIP
Crafted to perfection
ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 is styled for today, with a precision-crafted all-aluminum chassis finished with elegant diamond-cut anodized edges. Its refined looks are the perfect match for those who appreciate on-the-go versatility combined with peerless design.
MOBILITY
The 13" laptop with a 14" display
ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 is not only slim and light, but the new NanoEdge design gives it an ultracompact footprint, so you can enjoy all the benefits of a 14-inch FHD display in a chassis that's as small as many 13-inch laptops.
NANOEDGE DISPLAY
Unbounded vision with the NanoEdge display
Designed to give you the most screen area in the least physical space, the new four-sided NanoEdge display is simply breathtaking: it makes any visuals more immersive, with less distraction for your eyes. The ultraslim bezels are just 5mm thin at the sides for a near-borderless experience, and the crisp, clear, high-resolution screen gives you a beautiful creative workplace.
HINGE
Precision-engineered versatility
Featuring a precision-engineered mechanism, the versatile 360° ErgoLift hinge on ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 has a silky-smooth action that holds the display securely at any angle. This innovative hinge has a dual action that lifts and tilts the keyboard into the perfect typing position when the display is rotated into laptop mode. It also helps enhance the powerful audio, by creating extra space underneath the laptop.
PERFORMANCE
Breeze through your tasks all day long
Featuring powerful latest Intel® processors, ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 delivers great performance for popular apps, with extraordinary battery life. Combined with the full power of G Suite and other productivity apps from the Google Play store, ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 lets you breeze through all your everyday tasks on the go. The power-efficient ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 is designed to last for up to 10 hours on a single charge, so you can work or play throughout the day while you're on the move.
CONNECTIVITY
USB-C for ultimate flexibility
Two full-function reversible USB 3.1 Gen 1 Type-C™ (USB-C™) ports make it easy to charge your ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 or connect it to devices and external displays. For maximum convenience and compatibility, there's also a standard USB 3.1 Gen 1 Type-A port, and a microSD slot makes it easy to add extra storage.
WI-FI
Faster, more stable Wi-Fi connections
ASUS Chromebook Flip C434 includes dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi for strong, stable signals and fast data-transmission speeds. As an added advantage, 802.11ac Wi-Fi is less prone to interference from other wireless devices operating on the same frequency band.

Description:
HPE Ethernet 10Gb 2-port 562FLR-SFP+ Adapter - PCI Express 3.0 x8 - 2 Port(s) - Optical Fiber - 10GBase-X - FlexibleLOM 562FLR-SFP+ADPT PL=SI
The HPE Ethernet 10Gb 2-port 562FLR-SFP+ adapter, featuring the next generation of 10Gb Ethernet integration offering a single chip solution on a FlexibleLOM form factor, further reducing power requirements for 2 ports of 10Gb Ethernet. It is designed for use with HPE ProLiant Gen8 Rack and Scale-Out servers.

The HPE 562FLR dual-port design is ideal for high performance computing, server virtualization, security, server consolidation, and other applications requiring highest throughput. The total aggregate throughput of 20Gb meets the needs for customers desiring highest bandwidth.

The HPE 562FLR supports SR-IOV and enterprise class features such as Receive Side Scaling (RSS), Jumbo frames, PXE boot, Checksum and segmentation offload, and time stamping (IEEE 1588) along with virtualization features such as VMware NetQueue, Microsoft VMQ and Intel Virtualization Technology for Connectivity (VT-c).
